I"µ<h2 id="install-jekyll-on-windows7">Install Jekyll on Windows7</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Install <a href="https://rubyinstaller.org/downloads/" target="_blank">Ruby+Devkit</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Install Jekyll and Bundler gems through RubyGems</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem install jekyll bundler
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="command">Command</h2>

<p>Creates a new Jekyll site scaffold in PATH</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>jekyll new
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Change into your new directory</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>cd new-site
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Change Gemfile and _config.ymlï¼Œ  run</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>bundle install
bundle
</code></pre></div></div>

